Lanys T'Vyl.</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufelishannasecretlight.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Felishanna Secretlight</A> at: 6/4/01 6:07:41 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uyayger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yayger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t d00d!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(6/5/01 12:31:30 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ragefire: Lets make some rules.</span><hr size=1> Sounds like your both trying to say the same thing in a different way.<br>
